\c 18
\s Sungano pakati paAhabhi naJehoshafati, kufa kwaAhabhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehoshafati waiva nefuma nerukudzo zvizhinji; uye wakawanirana naAhabhi.
\v 2 Zvino pakupera kwemakore wakaburukira kuna Ahabhi kuSamaria. Ahabhi ndokumuuraira iye nevanhu vaaiva navo makwai nenzombe zvizhinji, ndokumunyengetedza kukwira kuRamoti-Giriyadhi.
\v 3 Zvino Ahabhi mambo waIsraeri wakati kuna Jehoshafati mambo waJudha: Muchaenda neni Ramoti-Giriyadhi here? Iye ndokuti kwaari: Ini \add ndakaita\add* sewe, nevanhu vangu sevanhu vako; uye tichava newe pahondo.
\v 4 Zvino Jehoshafati wakati kuna mambo waIsraeri: Bvunza hako nhasi shoko raJehovha.
\p
\v 5 Zvino mambo waIsraeri wakaunganidza kubva pavaporofita varume mazana mana, ndokuti kwavari: Tiende kuRamoti-Giriyadhi here kuhondo, kana ndirege? Ivo vakati: Kwirai nokuti Mwari acharipa muruoko rwamambo.
\v 6 Asi Jehoshafati wakati: Hakuchina umwe muporofita waJehovha pano here, kuti timubvunze?
\v 7 Mambo waIsraeri ndokuti kuna Jehoshafati, umwe murume achiko, watingabvunza naye \add kuda\add* kwaJehovha, asi ini ndinomuvenga, nokuti haatongoporofiti zvakanaka pamusoro pangu, asi mazuva ese zvakaipa; iye Mikaya mwanakomana waImira. Jehoshafati ndokuti: Mambo ngaarege kureva saizvozvo.
\v 8 Zvino mambo waIsraeri wakadana umwe mutenwa, ndokuti: Kurumidza uvinge Mikaya mwanakomana waImira.
\p
\v 9 Zvino mambo waIsraeri naJehoshafati mambo waJudha vaiva vagere umwe neumwe pachigaro chake cheushe, vakapfeka nguvo refu, uye vagere paburiro panopinda pasuwo reSamaria; vaporofita vese ndokuporofita pamberi pavo.
\v 10 Zvino Zedhekia mwanakomana waKenaana waiva azviitira nyanga dzematare, ndokuti: Ndizvo zvinoreva Jehovha: Neidzi muchatunga vaSiriya kusvikira mavapedza.
\v 11 Nevamwe vaporofita vese vakaporofita saizvozvo, vachiti: Kwirai kuRamoti-Giriyadhi mubudirire, nokuti Jehovha acharipa muruoko rwamambo.
\p
\v 12 Zvino nhume yakaenda kunodana Mikaya yakataura kwaari ichiti: Tarira, mashoko evaporofita akanaka kuna mambo uye muromo umwe; naizvozvo shoko renyu ngarive haro sereumwe wavo, mutaurewo zvakanaka.
\v 13 Mikaya ndokuti: NaJehovha mupenyu, zvirokwazvo Mwari wangu zvaachareva, izvozvo ndichataura.
\v 14 Zvino asvika kuna mambo, mambo wakati kwaari: Mikaya, tiende kuRamoti-Giriyadhi kuhondo here, kana ndirege? Iye ndokuti: Kwirai, muchabudirira; uye vachapiwa muruoko rwenyu.
\v 15 Mambo ndokuti kwaari: Ndichakupikisa kangani kuti urege kundiudza chinhu asi chokwadi muzita raJehovha?
\v 16 Iye ndokuti: Ndaona Israeri wese akapararira pamakomo semakwai asina mufudzi; Jehovha ndokuti: Ava havana tenzi, umwe neumwe ngaadzokere kumba kwake nerugare.
\v 17 Mambo waIsraeri ndokuti kuna Jehoshafati: Handina kukuudza here: Haangaporofiti zvakanaka pamusoro pangu, asi zvakaipa chete?
\v 18 Zvino wakati: Naizvozvo inzwai shoko raJehovha: Ndakaona Jehovha agere pachigaro chake cheushe, nehondo yese yekumatenga imire kurudyi rwake nekuruboshwe rwake.
\v 19 Jehovha ndokuti: Ndiani achakwezva Ahabhi mambo waIsraeri kuti akwire agowa paRamoti-Giriyadhi? Zvino umwe wakataura seizvi, umwe seizvi.
\v 20 Zvino mweya wakabuda, ndokumira pamberi paJehovha, ndokuti: Ini ndichanomukwezva. Jehovha ndokuti kwaari: Nei?
\v 21 Iye ndokuti: Ndichabuda ndigova mweya wenhema mumuromo wevaporofita vake vese. Iye ndokuti: uchakwezva, uye uchagona, buda ugoita saizvozvo.
\v 22 Naizvozvo zvino, tarirai, Jehovha waisa mweya wenhema mumuromo wevaporofita venyu ava, uye Jehovha wakataura zvakaipa pamusoro penyu.
\p
\v 23 Zvino Zedhekia mwanakomana waKenaana wakaswedera ndokurova Mikaya padama, ndokuti: Mweya waJehovha wakapfuura nenzira ipi achibva kwandiri kuti ataura newe?
\v 24 Mikaya ndokuti: Tarira uchaona musi wauchapinda mukamuri remukati kuti uvande.
\v 25 Zvino mambo waIsraeri wakati: Torai Mikaya, mumudzosere kuna Amoni mubati weguta, nekuna Joashi mwanakomana wamambo
\v 26 Zvino muti: Ndizvo zvinoreva mambo: Pinzai uyu mutirongo, mumudyise chingwa chekutamburira nemvura yekutamburira, kusvika ndadzoka nerugare.
\v 27 Zvino Mikaya wakati: Kana mukadzoka zvekudzoka nerugare, Jehovha haana kutaura neni. Iye ndokuti: Teererai imwi vanhu mese.
\p
\v 28 Naizvozvo mambo waIsraeri naJehoshafati mambo waJudha vakakwira kuRamoti-Giriyadhi.
\v 29 Zvino mambo waIsraeri wakati kuna Jehoshafati: Ndichazvivanza chimiro ndipinde pahondo; asi iwe pfeka nguvo refu dzako. Mambo waIsraeri ndokuzvivanza chimiro, zvino vakapinda pahondo.
\v 30 Zvino mambo weSiriya waiva araira misoro yengoro yaaiva nayo achiti: Regai kurwa nemudiki kana nemukuru, asi namambo waIsraeri chete.
\v 31 Zvino zvakaitika misoro yengoro payakaona Jehoshafati, kuti vakati: Ndimambo waIsraeri. Naizvozvo vakamukomba ku\add mu\add*rwisa; asi Jehoshafati wakaridza mhere, Jehovha ndokumubatsira; Mwari ndokuvakwezva vakabva kwaari.
\v 32 Nokuti zvakaitika, kuti misoro yengoro payakaona kuti waiva asiri mambo waIsraeri, vakadzoka pakumutevera.
\v 33 Zvino umwe munhu wakahwembura uta asina waakananga ndokurova mambo waIsraeri pakati pepakabatanidzwa nenguvo dzeutare. Zvino wakati kumufambisi wengoro: Tendeudza ruoko rwako, undibudise pahondo, nokuti ndakuvara.
\v 34 Zvino hondo yakawedzera pazuva iro; asi mambo waIsraeri wakaiva akatsigirwa mungoro akatarisana neVaSiriya kusvika madekwani. Zvino panguva yekuvira kwezuva wakafa.
